IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User bruno.kremel@gmail.com
PassCmd "~/imap-pass -g bruno.kremel@gmail.com"
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPAccount cern
Host imap.cern.ch
User bruno.kremel@cern.ch
PassCmd "~/imap-pass -g bruno.kremel@cern.ch"
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/mail/gmail/INBOX

IMAPStore cern-remote
Account cern

MaildirStore cern-local
Path ~/mail/cern/
Inbox ~/mail/cern/INBOX

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Bin" INBOX/*
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel cern
Master :cern-remote:
Slave :cern-local:
Patterns INBOX "Deleted Items" Outbox "Sent Items" "Drafts" INBOX/*
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
